title: Paris Saint-Germain women's player in custody following alleged attack on teammate
description: Paris Saint-Germain confirmed that French authorities took Aminata Diallo into custody following an alleged attack on teammate Kheira Hamraoui.
content:
Paris Saint-Germain confirmed that French authorities took women's club player Aminata Diallo into custody Wednesday morning after an attack on another one of the club's players.
